        <briefdescription>
<para>Set the given stimset parameter. </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>If you use this function in analysis functions be sure to use an event which happens <emphasis>before</emphasis> the stimset is read, for example <computeroutput>PRE_DAQ_EVENT</computeroutput>, <computeroutput>PRE_SET_EVENT</computeroutput> or <computeroutput>PRE_SWEEP_CONFIG_EVENT</computeroutput>. The last one is always called for each sweep before it is configured.</para>
<para><parameterlist kind="param"><parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
